thread.title: Rod Smith
thread.title_full: PACK & SEND Australia reviewed by Rod Smith

author: Rod Smith
title: Rod Smith
text:
I was impressed with how easy it was to book a cheap and insured freight package for a Gibson guitar from Perth WA to Sydney NSW.
In just four days the fragile instrument was delivered to my workplace, well before the 5pm deadline, in perfect condition.
The price - including insurance - was very reasonable. I'll happily recommend Pack & Send Australia.
